serviceAccountCredsSecretRef.description:
ServiceAccountCreds references a Kubernetes Secret key that contains a JSON document with service account credentials used to get an IAM token.

Expected JSON structure: {
  "subject-credentials": {
    "alg": "RS256",
    "private-key": "-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n<private-key>\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n",
    "kid": "<public-key-id>",
    "iss": "<issuer-service-account-id>",
    "sub": "<subject-service-account-id>"
  }
}
